          "role": "assistant",
          "content": "Punjab Enforcement and Regulatory Authority (PERA) ki composition kuch is tarah hai: Authority ka chairman Punjab ka Chief Minister hota hai. Iske ilawa Authority mein top provincial officials shamil hain, jin mein Chief Secretary (jo Vice Chair hota hai), Senior Member Board of Revenue, aur Home, Finance, Local Government ke Secretaries shamil hain. Provincial Police Officer (IG Punjab) bhi member hota hai. Authority mein Punjab Assembly ke teen members hote hain, jin mein ek aurat bhi shamil hoti hai. Iske alawa, chaar independent experts private sector se hote hain. PERA ka apna Director General bhi hota hai jo Member/Secretary ke taur par kaam karta hai. Ye tamam members mil kar PERA ka governing body banate hain. Yeh composition multi-disciplinary aur high-level hai jo Punjab ke mukhtalif sectors se logon par mushtamil hai.",
